{"tid":1472032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有答案] 到底點解每次行動升級後，手足都會嘈起黎","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:04:54.000Z","uid":2978,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"56e22a2800ae0c0bd1f4031351df5df6d407f872","tid":1472032,"uid":2978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:28:04.000Z","msg":"有位哈佛巴打就開左個post，當中提及到集體智慧呢一點，而我都十分贊成佢文章所寫既野。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果仲未睇既話，歡迎睇左先</span><br />\n(連載長文 代post) 哈佛社會學博士生給連登仔的信<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470587</a><br />\n<br />\n點解每次行動升級後或者去到某一啲過激位<br />\n容許我用勇武同和理非呢個TERM，佢地兩邊都會嘈起黎，而且意見有分歧？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁係因為大家仲未有共識</span></span>，<ins>亦係文中所指出既野「大家行事請要有一個機制，如投票，而投票結果必須被專重。」</ins>，「當然，小決定無需進行公投，但大方向最好<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>有共識後就唔好去違反</ins></span>。勇武前線各自爬山既行動大方向同底線，最好都事先同和理非有共識先，<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">咁樣就可以最大化集體智慧既益處</span></ins>。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十分之重要</span></span>，當中既共識並唔係叫大家建立大台(例如:決定下一步應做乜，再投票)，而係對於邊啲唔做得係有共識(例如:71立法會不破壞文物)。<br />\n<br />\n基於哈佛巴打所提出既點，我再闡述一下，共識應該要具體化，即係清楚例明邊一個情況係唔可以做某啲事。<br />\n<br />\n以下我會舉出幾個詳細既情況，而基於呢一啲情況，進行投票。<br />\n<br />\n而我都深明連登支持既野唔等於大部分示威者都支持，有發過夢既人就知現場同連登既氣氛係十分之唔同，所以都希望作為一個參考。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">情況一</span></strong></ins>：<br />\n如有路人經過影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />禮貌地行前要求佢地唔好影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大聲叫佢地咪撚影<br />\n<br />\n如途人屢勸不改繼續影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />詢問影大頭還是全景照<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接搶佢手機／用LASER POINTER射佢<br />\n<br />\n如途人惡言相向進而出手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五花大綁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接打柒佢<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">情況二</span></strong></ins>：<br />\n如司機對封路不耐煩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />禮貌地行前講對唔住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大聲叫佢收皮<br />\n<br />\n如司機自行拆除路障<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由佢拆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阻止佢<br />\n<br />\n如司機直接用車撞路障(有機會對手足造成危險)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sing hallelujah to the lord<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打柒佢<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">情況三</span></strong></ins>：<br />\n如懷疑有狗落單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五花大綁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接打柒佢<br />\n提醒：如有狗被善意對待（五花大綁／被人阻止打佢）係有機會開槍黎正當自衛<br />\n<br />\n如已FC係狗而已落單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五花大綁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接打柒佢<br />\n<br />\n我作左３個最簡單既情況，而最好每一個情況都係咁仔細，先會清楚從而都建立到共識。<br />\n我會係下面再留ＣＭ，從而進行投票。我明白有Ｄ題目既答案未必係咁二元，但都好過冇共識<br />\n<br />\n如果建立到共識即雙方沒有被強逼而已同意下，勇武同和理非就唔會再因某啲過激既位而再嘈起上黎，呢一樣野對成個運動都好大幫助，停止左分化互屌而繼續向前。<br />\n<br />\n最後一句，７２１　８０５　８１１<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025ab68edc69cec3da03c6ab751699a9e14687f2","tid":1472032,"uid":2978,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"情況一：<br />\n如有路人經過影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />禮貌地行前要求佢地唔好影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大聲叫佢地咪撚影"},{"pid":"9283e77f15021f803eacee7034e4b57b225880b3","tid":1472032,"uid":2978,"like":45,"dislike":13,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"025ab68edc69cec3da03c6ab751699a9e14687f2","tid":1472032,"uid":2978,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"情況一：<br />\n如有路人經過影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />禮貌地行前要求佢地唔好影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大聲叫佢地咪撚影"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:28:29.000Z","msg":"如途人屢勸不改繼續影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />詢問影大頭還是全景照<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接搶佢手機／用LASER POINTER射佢"},{"pid":"a69288c290a6adaf6c16a275e673b11c3e2df369","tid":1472032,"uid":2978,"like":40,"dislike":19,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"9283e77f15021f803eacee7034e4b57b225880b3","tid":1472032,"uid":2978,"like":45,"dislike":13,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"025ab68edc69cec3da03c6ab751699a9e14687f2","tid":1472032,"uid":2978,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"情況一：<br />\n如有路人經過影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />禮貌地行前要求佢地唔好影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大聲叫佢地咪撚影"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:28:29.000Z","msg":"如途人屢勸不改繼續影相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />詢問影大頭還是全景照<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接搶佢手機／用LASER POINTER射佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"如途人惡言相向進而出手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五花大綁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接打柒佢"},{"pid":"a9a04022ddd33a637f04a12e2a9ef5d2676bab27","tid":1472032,"uid":2978,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:28:55.000